#: ../../source/private-data/private-data.md:70
msgid ""
"The Distributor might want to make private transactions with the Farmer and "
"Shipper to keep the terms of the trades confidential from the Wholesaler and"
" the Retailer (so as not to expose the markup they're charging)."
msgstr "分销商可能希望与农场主和发货人进行私人交易，以对批发商和零售商保密交易条款(以免暴露他们收取的加价)。"

#: ../../source/private-data/private-data.md:75
msgid ""
"The Distributor may also want to have a separate private data relationship "
"with the Wholesaler because it charges them a lower price than it does the "
"Retailer."
msgstr "分销商还可能希望与批发商建立单独的私有数据关系，因为它向批发商收取的价格比零售商低。"

#: ../../source/private-data/private-data.md:79
msgid ""
"The Wholesaler may also want to have a private data relationship with the "
"Retailer and the Shipper."
msgstr "批发商还可能希望与零售商和发货人建立私有数据关系。"

