#: ../../source/private-data/private-data.md:91
msgid ""
"Using this example, peers owned by the Distributor will have multiple "
"private databases inside their ledger which includes the private data from "
"the Distributor, Farmer and Shipper relationship and the Distributor and "
"Wholesaler relationship. Because these databases are kept separate from the "
"database that holds the channel ledger, private data is sometimes referred "
"to as \"SideDB\"."
msgstr ""
"使用此示例，分销商拥有的peer在其账本中拥有多个私有数据库，其中包括来自分销商、农民和发货人关系以及分销商和批发商关系的私有数据。因为这些数据库与保存通道账本的数据库是分开的，所以私有数据有时被称为“侧DB”。"

#: ../../source/private-data/private-data.md:102
msgid ""
"When private data collections are referenced in chaincode, the transaction "
"flow is slightly different in order to protect the confidentiality of the "
"private data as transactions are proposed, endorsed, and committed to the "
"ledger."
msgstr "当在链码中引用私有数据集合时，为了保护私有数据的机密性，在提案、背书的和提交到账本时，交易流程略有不同。"

#: ../../source/private-data/private-data.md:106
msgid ""
"For details on transaction flows that don't use private data refer to our "
"documentation on transaction flow."
msgstr "有关不使用私有数据的交易流程的详细信息，请参阅我们关于交易流程的文档。"

#: ../../source/private-data/private-data.md:145
msgid ""
"For very sensitive data, even the parties sharing the private data might "
"want --- or might be required by government regulations --- to periodically "
"\"purge\" the data on their peers, leaving behind a hash of the data on the "
"blockchain to serve as immutable evidence of the private data."
msgstr ""
"对于非常敏感的数据，即使共享私有数据的各方也可能希望(或政府法规要求)定期“清除”其peer的数据，留下区块链上的数据哈希作为私有数据的不可变证据。"

#: ../../source/private-data/private-data.md:150
msgid ""
"In some of these cases, the private data only needs to exist on the peer's "
"private database until it can be replicated into a database external to the "
"peer's blockchain. The data might also only need to exist on the peers until"
" a chaincode business process is done with it (trade settled, contract "
"fulfilled, etc)."
msgstr ""
"在某些情况下，私有数据只需要存在于peer的私有数据库上，直到可以将其复制到peer区块链外部的数据库中为止。数据也可能只需要存在于peer节点上，直到使用它完成链码业务流程(交易结算、合同履行等)。"

#: ../../source/private-data/private-data.md:155
msgid ""
"To support these use cases, private data can be purged if it has not been "
"modified for a configurable number of blocks. Purged private data cannot be "
"queried from chaincode, and is not available to other requesting peers."
msgstr "为了支持这些用例，如果私有数据没有为可配置的区块数量修改，则可以清除它。清除后的私有数据不能从链码查询，并且对其他的peer请求不可用。"

